      <item>
        <title>How to deploy subfolder to Github Pages</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;We can use &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;git subtree&lt;/code&gt; to do this. And also nest git commands to execute force push (&lt;a href=&quot;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12644855/how-do-i-reset-a-heroku-git-repository-to-its-initial-state/13403588#13403588&quot;&gt;Reference&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-bash highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;git push origin &lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;git subtree split --prefix subfolder-name-here master&lt;span class=&quot;sb&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;:gh-pages --force
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Put this command to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;package.json&lt;/code&gt; file like bellow.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-json highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&quot;name&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;My App&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&quot;dependencies&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&quot;scripts&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&quot;deploy&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;git push origin `git subtree split --prefix subfolder-name-here master`:gh-pages --force&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After that, we can use &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;npm run deploy&lt;/code&gt; command to deploy subfolder to &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;gh-pages&lt;/code&gt; branch.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
